  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>Delete</TypeRef> method destroys the standard output target object.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Important">
      <Paragraph>
        Targets are normally destroyed through <TypeRef>ILogTarget::unique_ptr</TypeRef> or the owning <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager">LogManager</PageRef>.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
